The Sunday Law Crisis - Program 2: Getting Ready Spiritually - Part 2 of "The Sunday Law Crisis: What You Need to Know". This shocking 5-part series explores Gods prophecy of an approaching mark" of the beast (see Revelation 13:16,17), the role of the Roman Catholic Church, the Sabbath vs. Sunday controversy, and how to prepare for the return of Jesus Christ.
